                    <div class="span12">
                        <h1>SMA takes to social media, addresses ACFT 2.0 concerns</h1>
                        <p class="small">By Thomas Brading, Army News Service<span>June 18, 2020</span></p>
                        <section class="alt-social-bar">
  <ul>
        <li class="social-button-sm twitter-button">
            <a rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" href="https://twitter.com/share?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.army.mil%2Farticle%2F236558%2Fsma_takes_to_social_media_addresses_acft_2_0_concerns&amp;text=SMA%20takes%20to%20social%20media%2C%20addresses%20ACFT%202.0%20concerns"><span>Share on Twitter</span></a>
