            <a rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" href="https://www.reddit.com/submit?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.army.mil%2Farticle%2F236558%2Fsma_takes_to_social_media_addresses_acft_2_0_concerns"><span>Share on Reddit</span></a>
